::Dollen::

         Dollen suddenly has another vision of the beautiful fem bot.  Oh
no....His vision showed danger........Was the beautiful bot really real???
If yes, could she be in trouble???  He cleared his mind of these thoughts,
although not wanting to, as the bot was the most beautiful thing he had ever
seen.  He looked back at GoldenEye, still waiting for her to answer his
question.
